<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .header img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 200px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #555555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #0066cc;
        }
        .content a.github {
            background-color: #333333;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="{{imageUrl}}" alt="Campus Connect">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Emergency: Service Failure Alert ðŸ’¥ðŸ’¥</h1>
            <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
            <p>We wanted to inform you that the service <strong>{{serviceName}}</strong> has been down for more than 10 minutes. This issue requires immediate attention.</p>
            <p>You can check the service status and details using the following links:</p>
            <p><a href="{{githubRepoUrl}}" target="_blank" class="github">GitHub Repo</a></p>
            <p><a href="{{deploymentUrl}}" target="_blank">Check Deployment</a></p>
            <p>We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause and appreciate your prompt action to resolve the issue.</p>
            <p>Thank you,</p>
            <p>The Campus Connect Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2024 Campus Connect. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
